{"data":[{"id":560371878,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"8ab914dbc7a8fd7c7de22eef446be89c","url_token":"liu-liu-39-68","name":"刘留","avatar_url":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-dbef790594bc12fd6572f9fb710ec500_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-dbef790594bc12fd6572f9fb710ec500_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/8ab914dbc7a8fd7c7de22eef446be89c","user_type":"people","headline":"机械女博士/女魔头/常年处在男女比例10:1的环境","badge":[],"gender":0,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":784,"is_followed":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560371878","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545832663,"updated_time":1545832663,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":0,"comment_count":0,"is_sticky":false,"admin_closed_comment":false,"comment_permission":"all","can_comment":{"reason":"","status":true},"reshipment_settings":"allowed","content":"\u003cp\u003e以下对话发生在去年，就是我我研三还没读博的时候。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我：老师我想写个综述\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e导师:你读了多少篇论文了\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我：没数过，几十篇得有了吧\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e导师：呵呵，你还是先去读论文吧\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e那时候的我很不忿，劳资也读了不少论文了（本专业论文并不太多），说几十篇也是谦虚一下，于是我不服气啊，又找老师说这个事情，然后老师让我写个构架，我憋了俩月没憋出来，这事情就搁置了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e这学期开学，看了一个子类的很多论文，然后给老师做了几次汇报，然后我才了解，当时真的是初生牛犊不怕虎。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e数学领域我不懂，但是这个肯定是个科学难题\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e什么是科学难题，就是许多人基于很多基础理论和研究都没搞出来的东西。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e就像我想写个综述，结果发现其实文献还没读透，站在现在的角度才觉得以前的自己知道的太少，其实现在知道的也少，只是比以前多点，距离普通科研人员都还差一大截。然后明白过一个道理，难题就是难题，许多比你聪明的人比你努力的都没解决，初入科研时候读了点文章就想着去解决难题，然后才发现自己真的是太自信了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e所以，我可能有点跑题了，我只是想说，你真的解决了你所说的这个难题么\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e再回到你的问题，这个问题你都解决了，还清华北大。。。其实我觉得哈佛可以聘请你当教授了。\u003c/p\u003e","editable_content":"","excerpt":"以下对话发生在去年，就是我我研三还没读博的时候。我：老师我想写个综述导师:你读了多少篇论文了我：没数过，几十篇得有了吧导师：呵呵，你还是先去读论文吧那时候的我很不忿，劳资也读了不少论文了（本专业论文并不太多），说几十篇也是谦虚一下，于是我…","collapsed_by":"nobody","collapse_reason":"","annotation_action":[],"mark_infos":[],"relevant_info":{"is_relevant":false,"relevant_type":"","relevant_text":""},"suggest_edit":{"reason":"","status":false,"tip":"","title":"","unnormal_details":{"status":"","description":"","reason":"","reason_id":0,"note":""},"url":""},"is_labeled":false,"reward_info":{"can_open_reward":false,"is_rewardable":false,"reward_member_count":0,"reward_total_money":0,"tagline":""},"relationship":{"is_author":false,"is_authorized":false,"is_nothelp":false,"is_thanked":false,"voting":0,"upvoted_followees":[]}}],"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment_permission%2Ccreated_time%2Cupdated_time%2Creview_info%2Crelevant_info%2Cquestion%2Cexcerpt%2Crelationship.is_authorized%2Cis_author%2Cvoting%2Cis_thanked%2Cis_nothelp%2Cis_labeled%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.mark_infos%5B%2A%5D.url%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.author.follower_count%2Cbadge%5B%2A%5D.topics\u0026limit=1\u0026offset=1858\u0026platform=desktop\u0026sort_by=default","previous":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment_permission%2Ccreated_time%2Cupdated_time%2Creview_info%2Crelevant_i